    <updated>2018-07-16T04:23:00.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>由于5月份的<a href="http://daughter.tonybai.com/2018/05/19/participate-in-the-3rd-poetry-and-distance-competition-2018/">“诗与远方青少年诗词”复赛晋级</a>，今天晚上我参加了在沈阳市星摩尔购物中心举行的“诗与远方青少年诗词沈阳市总决赛”。</p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201807/diary_20180715_3.jpg" alt="签到"></p>
