<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201807/diary_20180715_1.jpg" alt="答题中"></p>
<p>每组有5分钟答题时间，答题完毕后，在场下等待出成绩：</p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201807/diary_20180715_2.jpg" alt="等待成绩中"></p>
